    "Our study exclusively focuses on injection drug use.",
    "In contrast, the error analysis of ConText indicates its unsatisfactory performance in identifying temporality related to chronic conditions and risk factors, i.e., alcohol, and drugs in clinical notes.",
    "Additionally, while ConText explicitly identifies historical versus recent conditions, our question-answering system concentrates on extracting any temporal information regarding injection drug use, leaving the determination of whether the status is recent or historical to clinicians.",
    "Regarding the query group-last use, it is crucial to note that a patient may have multiple note entries, each with its own last use.",
    "Given our study's emphasis on extracting information from one clinical note at a time, the definition of-last use-is confined to-last use per note."
